The '''LSS 1000 Automatic''' [[Stuncuffs/Legends|Stun cuffs]] were a pair of modified handcuffs used during the period following the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] war. They were known as a more sophisticated version of the [[LSS 401 Stun Cuffs]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] kept a pair of these powerful [[Stuncuffs/Legends|stun cuffs]] aboard the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']].

